CommandLineHelp::global

"Glove $version

$copyright

A data acquisition, manipulation, and analysis program for X.

Because Glove fully supports the Multiple Document concept, 
it can be safely invoked from the command line or via a file manager 
as often as you like.

Usage:
glove [ filename ]

--help     prints this help
--version  prints version information"

